_calculatePurchaseReturn(uint256,uint256.details: given a token supply, connector balance, weight and a deposit amount (in the connector token), calculates the return for a given conversion (in the main token) Formula: Return = _supply * ((1 + _depositAmount / _connectorBalance) ^ (_connectorWeight / 1000000) - 1) _depositAmount = [ exp{ log((Number/_supply) + 1) / (_connectorWeight / 1000000) } - 1  ] * _connectorBalance
